trans-unit.source: ASP.NET server controls can implement customized persistence formats by using their own control builder.
trans-unit.target: ASP.NET server-kontroller kan implementera anpassade beständiga format genom att använda sina egna kontrollen builder.

trans-unit.source: This is done by creating a control builder class and adding a control builder attribute to the class.
trans-unit.target: Detta görs genom att skapa en kontroll builder klass och lägga till en kontroll builder-attributet i klassen.

trans-unit.source: Control builder objects are used when the page is parsed and compiled.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollen builder objekt används när sidan parsas och kompileras.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Implementing Custom Persistence](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/ac8e85a9-422e-49b8-98c0-5ade5853ea7c).
trans-unit.target: Mer information finns i [implementera anpassade beständiga](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/ac8e85a9-422e-49b8-98c0-5ade5853ea7c).
